{"title_page": "Surya Roshni Limited", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox company\n| name           = Surya Roshni Limited\n| logo   = Logo of Surya Roshni Limited, as of 2014.png\n| logo_size = 180px\n| type   = [[Private company|Private]]\n| traded_as = {{NSE|SURYAROSNI}}<br>{{BSE|500336}}<br>ISIN: INE335A01012\n| founder        = B.D. Agarwal\n| industry       = [[Lighting]], [[Mechanical fan|Fan]], [[Steel]], PVC Pipes\n| location       = [[Delhi]], [[India]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.surya.co.in/contact-us-lighting.php |title=Contact Information |publisher=Surya.co.in}}</ref><br />Steel Division: [[Bahadurgarh]], [[Haryana]]\n| key_people     = Jai Prakash Agarwal<br>([[Chairman]])<br />[[Raju Bista]]<br>([[Managing Director]])\n| area_served    = Worldwide\n| products       = Lighting, Steel, PVC Pipes, Fans  \n| revenue = {{increase}} {{INRConvert|6000|c}}\n| revenue_year = 2018-19\n| homepage        = {{URL|http://www.surya.co.in}} \n}}\n\n'''[[Laxmi Kanta Das|Surya Roshni Limited]]''' (formerly Prakash Surya Roshni Limited) is an [[India]]n [[Multinational corporation|multinational]] [[Mechanical fan|Fan]]s, [[Steel]], [[Lighting]], [[LED lamp|LED]], [http://surya.co.in/home-appliances Kitchen Appliances]  and [http://surya.co.in/pvc-pipes PVC Pipes] manufacturing company headquartered in [[Delhi]], India. Surya exports its products over 44 countries and has a turnover close to Rs. 5,975 crore<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.surya.co.in/corporate-history.php |title=Surya Roshni Ltd with $650 turnover and 44 countries export.}}</ref>Laxmi Kant\n\n==History==\nSurya Roshni Limited was established by B.D. Agarwal in 1973 as a tube making unit. Today it also manufactures LEDs, Lighting, PVC Fans.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.surya.co.in/corporate-history.php|title=Surya Roshni Ltd Corporate History}}</ref> The company's current chairman is the [[Padma Shri]] awardee Shri [[Jai prakash agarwal]].\n\n==Manufacturing Plants==\nSurya Roshni's Steel division is called '''Surya Steel Pipes''' with steel manufacturing plants in [[Bhuj]] ([[Gujarat]]), [[Gwalior]] ([[Madhya Pradesh]]) and its primary steel plant in [[Bahadurgarh]], [[Haryana]]. Surya started Commercial Production on 1 March 2017 at their new steel pipe plant with an investment of 70cr at Hindupur Industrial area, Dist anantapur, which is 100&nbsp;km away from Bangalore.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.surya.co.in/milestones/}}</ref> Surya's lighting plant is in [[Kashipur, Uttarakhand]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kashipur.in/business/surya-roshni-limited|title=Surya Roshni Limited Light manufacturing plant in Kashipur, Uttarakhand  }}</ref> and [[Gwalior]] ([[Madhya Pradesh]])\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Manufacturing companies based in Delhi]]\n[[Category:Steel companies of India]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox company\n| name           = Surya Roshni Limited\n| logo   = Logo of Surya Roshni Limited, as of 2014.png\n| logo_size = 180px\n| type   = [[Private company|Private]]\n| traded_as = {{NSE|SURYAROSNI}}<br>{{BSE|500336}}<br>ISIN: INE335A01012\n| founder        = B.D. Agarwal\n| industry       = [[Lighting]], [[Mechanical fan|Fan]], [[Steel]], PVC Pipes\n| location       = [[Delhi]], [[India]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.surya.co.in/contact-us-lighting.php |title=Contact Information |publisher=Surya.co.in}}</ref><br />Steel Division: [[Bahadurgarh]], [[Haryana]]\n| key_people     = Jai Prakash Agarwal<br>([[Chairman]])<br />[[Raju Bista]]<br>([[Managing Director]])\n| area_served    = Worldwide\n| products       = Lighting, Steel, PVC Pipes, Fans  \n| revenue = {{increase}} {{INRConvert|6000|c}}\n| revenue_year = 2018-19\n| homepage        = {{URL|http://www.surya.co.in}} \n}}\n\n'''[[Laxmi Kanta Das|Surya Roshni Limited]]''' (formerly Prakash Surya Roshni Limited) is an [[India]]n [[Multinational corporation|multinational]] [[Mechanical fan|Fan]]s, [[Steel]], [[Lighting]], [[LED lamp|LED]], [http://surya.co.in/home-appliances Kitchen Appliances]  and [http://surya.co.in/pvc-pipes PVC Pipes] manufacturing company headquartered in [[Delhi]], India. Surya exports its products over 44 countries and has a turnover close to Rs. 5,975 crore<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.surya.co.in/corporate-history.php |title=Surya Roshni Ltd with $650 turnover and 44 countries export.}}</ref>Laxmi Kant\n\n==History==\nSurya Roshni Limited was established by B.D. Agarwal in 1973 as a tube making unit. Today it also manufactures LEDs, Lighting, PVC Fans.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.surya.co.in/corporate-history.php|title=Surya Roshni Ltd Corporate History}}</ref> The company's current chairman is the [[Padma Shri]] awardee Shri [[Jai Prakash Agarwal]].\n\n==Manufacturing Plants==\nSurya Roshni's Steel division is called '''Surya Steel Pipes''' with steel manufacturing plants in [[Bhuj]] ([[Gujarat]]), [[Gwalior]] ([[Madhya Pradesh]]) and its primary steel plant in [[Bahadurgarh]], [[Haryana]]. Surya started Commercial Production on 1 March 2017 at their new steel pipe plant with an investment of 70cr at Hindupur Industrial area, Dist anantapur, which is 100&nbsp;km away from Bangalore.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.surya.co.in/milestones/}}</ref> Surya's lighting plant is in [[Kashipur, Uttarakhand]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kashipur.in/business/surya-roshni-limited|title=Surya Roshni Limited Light manufacturing plant in Kashipur, Uttarakhand  }}</ref> and [[Gwalior]] ([[Madhya Pradesh]])\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Manufacturing companies based in Delhi]]\n[[Category:Steel companies of India]]\n", "name_user": "Ziyush", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surya_Roshni_Limited"}
